{"tid":1701901,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"每年加家用7%，唔俾咁多得唔得","createTime":"2019-11-09T11:32:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T13:27:34.000Z","uid":237377,"like":6,"dislike":66,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"3697785ceb3d1f678addf1128334b3cec14514c0","tid":1701901,"uid":237377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T11:32:04.000Z","msg":"是咁的，本人係18 年ugrad,做咗一年野。呀爸話要加家用，一加就加7%，問點解要加家用超過通脹3.x%，佢話差餉電費好多野都唔跟通漲率，堅持要加咁多。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本人係文科窮L, 18年畢業，本身家用已佔30%人工，好鬼窮。<br />\n<br />\n又見老豆十幾年黎俾老母的家用都無加過，心諗點解我要加咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家有無咩理據可以俾我去講數，等我唔使加咁多家用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a91f061a9f8c29f71355b12c09a12fc696eb8361","tid":1701901,"uid":330472,"like":59,"dislike":1,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T11:33:13.000Z","msg":"問佢拎錢比首期"},{"pid":"43d7734be56ba277e9e656891814472a4c37eb0f","tid":1701901,"uid":2113,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T11:35:30.000Z","msg":"電費水費煤氣唔跟通漲..<br />\n但係因為使用量計算價格<br />\n我用少啲..食少啲..朝早又要返工..係屋企時間咁短<br />\n係咪家用可以唔加..反而要減家用先?"},{"pid":"56fd09177d6c7eb6ba54c249958c3f1587ae6d89","tid":1701901,"uid":88723,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T11:37:47.000Z","msg":"轉左工 人工少左 減家用"},{"pid":"d7f8dd51497b8f82b2d7200289ece2d757d34e93","tid":1701901,"uid":127177,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T11:38:05.000Z","msg":"隔離屋小學考第一個小明都唔需要俾家用,點解我要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"056b450cd34a88f093b5db0b222b529a527e935a","tid":1701901,"uid":210612,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T11:38:48.000Z","msg":"唔撚比 走"},{"pid":"84fa82720fedde0e00847c6055b1c5267490bf82","tid":1701901,"uid":3302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T11:39:11.000Z","msg":"應該拎左去叫雞<br />\n養兒防老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfd348c7342c5780076adfeb0537058fdbe24086","tid":1701901,"uid":12705,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T11:40:00.000Z","msg":"要理由㗎咩?<br />\n唔撚比咪唔撚比"},{"pid":"ed8d2d69b1b3e52652e69ea7b988a2d479bfc168","tid":1701901,"uid":201414,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T11:49:05.000Z","msg":"我唔撚加家用你吹得我脹 有本事趕我走囉 撚樣~"},{"pid":"d3c6db14bd13800414d3e13a3d753dc848dc5576","tid":1701901,"uid":72173,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T11:49:33.000Z","msg":"如果果到已經講緊六七八千蚊 <br />\n咁已經可以考慮同人夾搬出去<br />\n<br />\n你同屋企人講轉左工減人工<br />\n大把籍口唔撚比"},{"pid":"1df371220740b1617a2cb040242feb551a09de99","tid":1701901,"uid":34976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T11:57:23.000Z","msg":"你查撚返港燈/中電/煤氣近幾年每度比幾多重好，用多左就用多左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f073d5cb4372f89b6aaff86645b960456ab55c99","tid":1701901,"uid":40397,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:06:19.000Z","msg":"真係唔夠用就講囉，唔會傾唔掂既"},{"pid":"a71dd6e22e8a6d6a54924869bfd9f16e1d042215","tid":1701901,"uid":175540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:09:41.000Z","msg":"佢黃定藍定紅?"},{"pid":"9ee47526ca071ed9c5bd1a38ea8ecd47f38ea9ca","tid":1701901,"uid":5267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:15:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70b391a155b6fa53c2bc9d7225712d04fefa0e89","tid":1701901,"uid":160348,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:16:17.000Z","msg":"我老母轉黃後加咗10%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4960168ced277c29e63fe6d4427a4a9999d7b3a3","tid":1701901,"uid":127202,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:19:29.000Z","msg":"彩佢都有味<br />\n將啲錢掟落佢塊面到 大大聲同佢講<br />\n要就要